<http://ClimOO/climoo/imports/cco-imports> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                            owl:versionIRI <http://ClimOO/climoo/imports/cco-imports#2026-04-09> ;
                                            <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> """This file contains ClimOO Ontology imports from the Common Core Ontology suite (CCO). Imports were manually collected and revised.

Ontology source: CCO 1.7.
https://github.com/CommonCoreOntology/CommonCoreOntologies/releases/tag/v1.7-2024-11-03"""@en ;
                                            rdfs:comment """Two new releases of CCO, CCO 1.7 and CCO 2.0, have been made available in November 2024. CCO 2.0 provides a new IRI schema. SCO, ClimOO upper-level ontology, imports from a former release. CCO 1.5. Aiming to conform with SCO, ClimOO currently reuses CCO imports in compliance with SCO. As soon as updates are made available for those resources, ClimOO will align accordingly. 

https://github.com/CommonCoreOntology/CommonCoreOntologies/releases
https://w3id.org/sco/repo"""@en ;
                                            rdfs:seeAlso "https://github.com/CommonCoreOntology/CommonCoreOntologies" ;
                                            owl:versionInfo "2026-02-27" .

