                                                                        <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A Gain of Disposition in which some Independent Continuant becomes the bearer of some Function."@en .


###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfGenericallyDependentContinuant
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfGenericallyDependentContinuant> rdf:type owl:Class ;
