                                                                                              rdfs:label "Gain of Generically Dependent Continuant"@en ;
                                                                                              <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A Gain of Dependent Continuant wherein some Independent Continuant becomes the carrier of some Generically Dependent Continuant."@en ;
                                                                                              <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "A Person forms a Plan, A Person is initiated into a Religion, A photgraphic image is produced." .


###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfQuality
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfQuality> rdf:type owl:Class ;
