                                                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "A person becoming pregnant." .


###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfRealizableEntity
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfRealizableEntity> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfSpecificallyDependentContinuant> ,
